Program to find whether the entererd character either 
(1).Upper case letter
(2).Lower case letter
(3).A digit
Source code:
#include <stdio.h>
int main() 
{
    int ch;
scanf("%c",&ch);
if(ch>=65 && ch<=90)
{
    printf("%c is a upper case letter",ch);
}
if(ch>=97 && ch<=122)
{
    printf("%c is a lower case letter",ch);
}
if(ch>=48 && ch<=57)
{
    printf("%c is a digit",ch);
}

    return 0;
}
Output(1):
A
A is a upper case letter
Output(2):
b
b is a lower case letter
Output(3).
3
3 is a digit
